metadata.name: Gonzion #6
metadata.description:
Gonzion is a Non-Linear Iterated Function System rendered using a method similar to Fractal Flames of Electric Sheep fame.

Technological tendrils from beyond light-aeons draw ancient crystals, transmuted fungus, sentient sigils in fossilized dimensions and alien topologies.

It's not built to run on a (2022) mobile phone and has been known to crash some, but runs fine on others.

For higher resolution renders add "#N" to the URL, default N=2.

metadata.name: GOLENS #86
metadata.description:
"- May every star in the sky become a life?"
"- Yes, and I'll call them golens!

Have you ever noticed how morbid it is? People make wishes to shooting stars. Do they not understand? What can a star, desperate, in the midst of a suicidal fall, give you? She just wants to die at ocean.

Tonight the stars will not fall, they will rise, and they'll be watching our end, we'll die in the ocean.


GOLENS are generative created.
- 15 Body Parts ( not on traits )
- 6 Hierarchy Grades.
- 9 Sky.
- 4 Weathers.
- 9 Powers.


by Gen Doodler | twitter.com/GenDoodler

metadata.name: Resilience  #44
metadata.description:
Resilience is a collection of endless architectures.
In a resilient generative system composed of multiple compatible parts, real-time information exchange enables open reconfigurations and continuous discrete adjustments. Sometimes vague and fuzzy, sometimes real and tangible, they reveal different readings of architectural complexity and scale: from city plans to floor plans and details to sections and elevations.

Resilience comes in a variety of polychrome palettes, ascii glyphs, and styles. 
To enjoy it in full-screen mode, press the left mouse button in live mode, for a monochrome look press 'b'. Made with P5js.

Resilience Generative Token by @grasser_alex 2022

metadata.name: brushstroke #72
metadata.description:
Brushstroke is an algorithm to form a minimal, modern, artistic paint on a canvas. It mimics a painter's hand gesture to apply different types of strokes. Those strokes may vary from thin straight lines to fat curvy arcs. The direction of the strokes may change for each stroke or not. There may be an excessive amount of them as there may be just several. Strokes may intersect and form a group. It generates color palettes as an artist does. There are more than twenty parameters that give variety to pieces. 

Brushstroke is built on the p5.js library. As a way of saying thanks, you will contribute to the Processing Foundation by collecting this work.

metadata.name: Particularization #83
metadata.description:
‚ÄúParticularization‚Äù is the seventh collection released as a part of NeoMent's "Abandoned Reality" series.

All concepts can be viewed from different levels. You can focus on the details, leaving out the generalized result but understanding the finer points. Or you could emphasize the concept as a whole, comprehending it well overall but missing out on the specifics. It's impossible to choose both, you have to figure out which approach works best for each scenario.

metadata.name: Chaos Cluster #17
Mythologic #35
metadata.description:
"Mythologic" is part of the fxhash interactive minting experience at The Ever-Evolving World of Art, Art Basel Hong-Kong, 2022.

Mythologic is a project derived from cloud series, Cloud Atlas and Requiem: Cloud on fxhash. In the series, lines and circles are used in an organics movement like Cloud Hands, which is a move of Tai Chi. Practitioners move their hands slowly and smoothly, make circles and rotate with extreme concentrating. In Chinese we said ‚Äúfloating clouds and flowing water‚Äù to describe calligraphers‚Äô freely flowing style of writing. Chi is a very important for oriental artists, and for genart as well. In the series, lines and circles start from one position to another, and develop with organic rotations and movements, like practicing Tai Chi on the canvas. 

Mythologic was inspired from ‚ÄúClassic of Mountains and Seas‚Äù, also known as Shan Hai Jing, is a Chinese classic text and a compilation of mythic geography and beasts. 

‚ÄúThere is a beast that looks like a fox with nine tails.‚Äù 
‚ÄúHuangbei: it is a beetle with meat like a tadpole, but with a head and a tail‚Äù 
‚ÄúThe beast has the body of a fish but the wings of a bird‚Äù 

There are many incredible creatures in the text which describe the oriental fantasy. The idea of Mythologic is to present an illustrated handbook with random generated paintings, each one is like a framed badge, to memorize the glorious age. It uses the "cloud hands" technique in every parts of this piece, the center, the circle and the frame. They are all the same algorithm but perform variety with different density and components. Gold, Silver, Copper, Jade and Ruby colors as noble symbol of treasure in Chinese culture. 

This project use p5js. 

Press 'S' to save pictures.

Thanks to the support of Yi-Wen Lin in this project.

metadata.name: Omega Point #100
metadata.description:
In the collapsing universe approaching singularity, the last remaining cybernetic organisms encounter the state of infinite knowledge, information, and computational resources.
Although the living creatures in the Omega Point are destined for imminent destruction, they experience infinite life.

----

Live mode controls:
'r' - change resolution
's' - save PNG
'space' - improve image quality
'f' - increase rendering speed

The image quality gradually improves over time, up to a certain level. To reach the maximum quality, press 'space'.
The rendering speed is reduced by default - press 'f' for the maximum speed.

Rendering may be GPU intensive.
Requires WebGL2.
